narratives.question_text: What was valuable about this class, either in format or content?
comments: I learn basic and advance music composition in this class which push me further. I got the big assignment that I never thing that I can make it happen but because of Matthew give us the good encouragement and shared his valuable experience as a composer it happen. :)

narratives.question_text: Are there adjustments, additions or deletions that might be beneficial?
Were there any particular challenges that were difficult to overcome?
comments: The assignment is hard but good for me. :) Making music for me inspiration is important but here i don't have time to find one easily.

narratives.question_text: Do you have any comments about the teaching/learning environment?
comments: LOVE IT. I love small group class because we can listen to my pears composition and talk about it.
